             was indicted for <rs id="t17950114-14-off80" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17950114-14-off80" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17950114-14-off80" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17950114-14-cd81" type="crimeDate">18th of December</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17950114-14-off80 t17950114-14-cd81"></join>, fourteen pounds weight of raw coffee, value 10s.
            </rs> the goods of 
               <persName id="t17950114-14-victim158" type="victimName">
                  Thomas 
                  Hanson
               <interp inst="t17950114-14-victim158" type="surname" value="Hanson"></interp>
