                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17950114-14-defend157 t17950114-14-punish87"></join>
               Publickly Whipped
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the London Jury before the Lord CHIEF BARON.</p>
